snippet.title: Problem Here - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Problem Here Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1550030/Problem_Here/

Hello, and the big day has come! Are you ready to be scared and have a lot of fun with your friends? Problem Here is currently accessible on Steam. For any bugs you may encounter during the game, please do not forget to contact us. You can make such shares in the #👷-bug-report  section of our Discord channel. You can also send us your game suggestions in the #📝suggestion-öneri  section. Thank you for supporting us. Have fun!

EN: You have to make the right decisions to succeed in Problem Here, where you can play up to a maximum of 6 people. It’s little time left to enter the atmosphere, but there are some problems. As a crew, you must manage to get into the atmosphere!

Don't forget to add to your wish list.

TR: Maksimum 6 kişiye kadar oynayabileceğiniz Problem Here'da başarılı olmak için doğru kararlar vermelisiniz. Atmosfere girmeye az bir süre kaldı, ancak bazı problemler var. Mürettebat olarak atmosfere girmeyi başarmalısınız!

İstek listenize eklemeyi unutmayın.

Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1550030/Problem_Here
Discord : https://discord.gg/k2W7wvfwsb
Twitter : https://twitter.com/deeprangestudio
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/deeprangestudio/
